Faster than light travel is possible through wormholes. However they take a huge amount of power.
-planets can only really have one.
-need to rely on network
-standard to packet forward
-main character is a scientist
-had a sudden idea while a planet was being Terra formed
-had access to a fusion reactor(s) before colonization
-punches direct hole and finds its slower than expected.
-have to figure out why.
